Package: kiwisR
Title: A Wrapper for Querying KISTERS WISKI Databases via the KiWIS API
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ryan",
           family = "Whaley",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rdgwhaley@gmail.com")
Description: A wrapper for querying KISTERS WISKI databases via the KiWIS REST API. 
  Contains a list of default databases (called 'hubs') and also allows users to provide
  their own KiWIS URL. Supports the entire query process- from metadata to specific time series
  values. All data is returned as tidy tibbles.
